# 🤖 Smart EduBot: AI Chatbot for Educational Support

Smart EduBot is an intelligent chatbot designed to provide instant assistance for educational queries. It supports students, parents, and academic staff by answering frequently asked questions about admissions, fees, exam schedules, academic calendars, syllabus, and more.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Handles inquiries about:
  - ✅ Admissions & Courses
  - 💰 Fee Structure
  - 🗓️ Academic Calendar & Exam Schedules
  - 📚 Syllabus and Study Materials
  - 🎓 Eligibility and Deadlines
- Text-to-Speech (TTS) replies using browser's speech engine
- Web-based chat interface
- JSON & SQLite powered FAQs
- Optional ML-based intent detection with `nlu_model.pkl`

---

## 🛠️ Technology Stack

| Component     | Tech                     |
|---------------|--------------------------|
| Frontend      | HTML, CSS, JavaScript    |
| Backend       | Python (Flask)           |
| Chat Logic    | Rule-based + JSON + ML (optional) |
| Database      | SQLite / JSON            |
| TTS           | Web Speech API (JS)      |

